To install on a new machine:

    $ mkvirtualenv pelican
    $ pip install pelican ghp-import
    $ cd /PATH/TO/SITE/
    $ setvirtualenvproject

To develop:

    $ make dev-server
    $ # edit site to your liking

To deploy:

    $ git add ...
    $ git commit ...
    Push changes to production? [Yes/no] Y
    Changes committed to release branch and pushed to production.
    $


